# Change Documentation Required

- For every change, create a doc using the right template (feature/modification/fix).
- Include what/why/how, alternatives, impacts, testing, and links to edited files.
- Reference the change doc in commit messages and PR descriptions.

How:
- Copy from templates and file under docs/changes/[category]/YYYY-MM-DD_title.md
- Use Feature/Modification/Fix/Architecture templates.

